# Mapping My Resume to Cloud Security, FinOps, Governance & Cloud Operations

This file connects my resume directly to modern cloud roles so recruiters clearly understand how my background transfers.

---

# 1. Cloud Security & Zero Trust Mapping

### Resume Highlights
- Command Security Manager over 3,500 personnel
- SCIF access, background checks, credentialing
- Insider threat prevention, OPSEC, audit controls
- DoD/NSA/DOJ/Federal compliance
- RMF & IA exposure
- IT & cybersecurity oversight

### Cloud Alignment
- IAM governance
- Zero Trust access control
- Security baselines (CIS)
- Policy enforcement & compliance
- Identity governance automation
- Incident response and risk mitigation
- Cloud security posture principles

